{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to VRShogiMates, your gateway to a captivating virtual realm of classic board games! As a solo developer's passion project, this app delivers an unparalleled experience featuring Shogi, Chu Shogi, Chess, Xiangqi, and the unique Gungi from Hunter X Hunter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge opponents worldwide in real-time or correspondence (turn-based) matches. Whether facing friends or discovering new adversaries, the global multiplayer functionality ensures a dynamic and engaging experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New to these intricate games? No problem! VRShogiMates provides comprehensive rules, instructions, and a game record for each game type to help you learn. Explore the rules, grasp essential strategies, and elevate your skills!<br><br>Note: Please use Steam Link as Virtual Desktop causes issues with the inputs (Can be manually fixed through Steam VR).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Regular Updates and Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">My commitment doesn't end at launch. Expect continuous updates, bug fixes, performance enhancements, and exciting new features driven by valuable feedback from you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Highlights</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture into the unexplored VR realms of Shogi, Chu Shogi, Xiangqi, and Gungi - experiences currently not offered by any other VR app on the market! The last game type, Gungi, brings a touch of fantasy to your gaming repertoire. It\u2019s refreshingly different from other board games, check it out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on this virtual journey, where tradition meets innovation, and every move is a step towards victory. VRShogiMates is not just a game; it's a portal to a world where strategy, competition, and community converge. Join us and redefine your board gaming experience!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730623179","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915300/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730623179","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915300/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730623179","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915300/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730623179","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3175640,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to VRShogiMates, your gateway to a captivating virtual realm of classic board games! As a solo developer's passion project, this app delivers an unparalleled experience featuring Shogi, Chu Shogi, Chess, Xiangqi, and the unique Gungi from Hunter X Hunter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge opponents worldwide in real-time or correspondence (turn-based) matches. Whether facing friends or discovering new adversaries, the global multiplayer functionality ensures a dynamic and engaging experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New to these intricate games? No problem! VRShogiMates provides comprehensive rules, instructions, and a game record for each game type to help you learn. Explore the rules, grasp essential strategies, and elevate your skills!<br><br>Note: Please use Steam Link as Virtual Desktop causes issues with the inputs (Can be manually fixed through Steam VR).</p><p 